5000|$|The Institute of Professional Representatives {{before the}} <b>European</b> <b>Patent</b> Office, {{also known as}} <b>European</b> <b>Patent</b> Institute (epi), is a {{professional}} association of <b>European</b> <b>patent</b> attorneys and an international non-governmental public law corporation. It was founded on October 21, 1977 by the Administrative Council of the <b>European</b> <b>Patent</b> Organisation. All <b>European</b> <b>patent</b> attorneys, i.e. all persons entitled to act as professional representatives before the EPO (by virtue of either the European qualifying examination or the provisions of [...] ), {{are members of the}} Institute.|$|R
